WEBVTT

00:13:58.229 --> 00:14:02.063
I don't believe our species
can survive unless we fix this.

00:14:02.087 --> 00:14:04.377
We cannot have a society

00:14:04.401 --> 00:14:07.362
in which, if two people
wish to communicate,

00:14:07.386 --> 00:14:10.826
the only way that can happen
is if it's financed by a third person

00:14:10.850 --> 00:14:13.196
who wishes to manipulate them.

00:14:13.220 --> 00:14:19.458
(Applause)

00:14:23.077 --> 00:14:24.228
(Applause ends)

00:14:24.942 --> 00:14:27.887
In the meantime,
if the companies won't change,

00:14:27.911 --> 00:14:29.577
delete your accounts, OK?

00:14:29.601 --> 00:14:30.870
(Laughter)